         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne Juni ¶ German for June. ¶  ¶ 11. 1858 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ The cost of one plate, containing Plants for a scientific work, is ten pounds Strlg ¶ Sterling. ¶  ¶ and ¶  ¶ eight ¶  ¶ pounds with less sha...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">58.06.11</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Ludwig Becker</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">EFOL L3, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter attached to a printed copy of a drawing of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Marianthus bignoniaceus</seg>
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>F.M. drawn by Ludwig Becker and printed by Hamel &amp; Locher. The drawing is an earlier version, printed in reverse, more heavily shaded and with some differences in the presentation, of the lithograph published as Plate 10 in B62.03.03; the latter is, however, stated to have been lithographed by F. Schoenfeld, not Becker, from a drawing by Becker, and the pinter's name is given as Hamel &amp; Co.</p>
               </note>Melbourne Juni<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>German for June.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>11. 1858</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The cost of one plate, containing Plants for a scientific work, is ten pounds Strlg<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sterling.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">eight</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>pounds with less shading; herein is included:</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">1) The original drawing of the Specimen,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Annotation by M at bottom of printed drawing: 'Tender of L Becker Esq £10. with less shading<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <hi rend="underline">£</hi>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <hi rend="underline">8</hi>
                        </seg>'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">2) The Analysis of each plant,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">3) The transfering one stone and</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">4) Superintending the printing etc:</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your most obedient</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ludwig Becker.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to J. O'Shanassy, 21 August 1858<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(In this edition is 58-08-21a).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr F. Mueller.</p>
         </div>
